  <brief_title>Study of the Immunogenicity and Efficacy of HBsAg Vaccine in Combination With Standard Antiviral Therapy With HB110E</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of the Immunogenicity and Efficacy of HBsAg Vaccine in Combination With Standard Antiviral Therapy in Patients Who Have Been Treated With HB110E Hepatitis B DNA Vaccine</official_title>
