  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the immunogenicity and efficacy of HBsAg Vaccine in
      combination with Entecavir in patients who have been treated with HB110E HBV DNA vaccine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
